* GF180MCU-D scaffold-only class-A common-source RF PA.
* Pins: gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias
* Status: topology seed only; matching, bias, and finite-Q networks must be
* re-sized before using simulation results for design decisions.
.subckt {{netlist_name}} gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias

* Output device.
MMOUT drain gate gnda gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ M1_L }}u w={{ M1_W }}u m={{ M1_M }}

* Input coupling and gate bias.
CINBLK rfin gate_in {{ Cin_value }}
RGSTOP gate_in gate {{ Rg_value }}
RBIAS gate vbias {{ Rbias_value }}

* Idealized RF choke and damped output tank seed near 250 MHz.
LRFC vdda drain 200n
RRFC vdda drain 10k
RTANK drain tank 5
LTANK tank tank_c 40.5n
CTANK tank_c gnda 10p

* AC-coupled single-ended output.
COUT drain rfout {{ Cout_value }}
ROUTLEAK rfout gnda 1G

.ends {{netlist_name}}
